OL,3,C'Crisis' of diagnosis delays for
OL,4,Cchildren with additional learning needs
OL,6,FA new system to help families with
OL,7,Fchildren with additional learning
OL,8,Fneeds has been announced by the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment.
OL,11,FIt comes as families say there is a
OL,12,F'crisis' of diagnosis delays for
OL,13,Fchildren with additional learning
OL,14,Fneeds.
OL,16,FRebecca Gilroy is a mum to a daughter
OL,17,Fwith additional learning needs and
OL,18,Fsays her family waited two years for
OL,19,Fher daughter to be diagnosed.
