OL,3,C'Crisis' of diagnosis delays for
OL,4,Cchildren with additional learning needs
OL,6,F"What's crucial is, until they have
OL,7,Fthat diagnosis, they cannot go to the
OL,8,Fcorrect provision," Ms Gilroy said.
OL,10,FMs Gilroy says her daughter Milly is
OL,11,Fone of the 'lucky' children who was
OL,12,Fofficially diagnosed by the age of
OL,13,Ffive, compared to those who wait even
OL,14,Flonger.
OL,16,FMilly is now in a school to best suit
OL,17,Fher needs, but it hasn't been without
OL,18,Fits challenges.
