OL,3,C'Crisis' of diagnosis delays for
OL,4,Cchildren with additional learning needs
OL,6,F"Milly is five now, I have fought
OL,7,Fevery single step of the way, as many
OL,8,Fparents do, to get the children in the
OL,9,Fright place," Ms Gilroy said.
OL,11,FMinisters say the new Parent and Carer
OL,12,Ftoolkit, announced on Wednesday, will
OL,13,Fmake it easier to access support and
OL,14,Funderstand their rights.
OL,16,FThe Welsh Government says a further
OL,17,F#8.2m in funding will go to councils
OL,18,Fthis year to help them deliver ALN
OL,19,Freforms.
