OL,3,C'Crisis' of diagnosis delays for
OL,4,Cchildren with additional learning needs
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Lynn Neagle MS
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're going to be doing
OL,8,Feverything we can to promote that with
OL,9,Fparents right across Wales.
OL,11,F"Because what we don't want is parents
OL,12,Fstruggling to get the information that
OL,13,Fthey need.
OL,15,F"We've co-produced this toolkit with
OL,16,Fparents so hopefully everyone will
OL,17,Funderstands what their entitlements
OL,18,Fare are."
